><p class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#2C1810]\">800</p><p class=\"text-[9px] uppercase font-black text-[#D4AF37]\">Families</p></div></div></div><a class=\"inline-block bg-[#2C1810] text-white px-10 py-4 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#D4AF37] transition-all shadow-xl\" href=\"/farmers\">Meet the Producers</a></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#2C1810] py-32 px-6 text-white overflow-hidden relative\"><svg class=\"absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-64 h-64 text-[#D4AF37] opacity-5 rotate-12\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20M2 12h20\"></path></svg><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-20 items-center\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-1 space-y-6\"><svg class=\"w-12 h-12 text-[#D4AF37] opacity-40\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20M2 12h20\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-serif italic leading-tight\">Industrial <br/> Scale.</h2><p class=\"text-stone-400 text-sm leading-loose\">Equipped with high-airflow Japanese roasting technology for global container-load exports.</p></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"p-10 border border-white/5 bg-white/5 rounded-sm space-y-6\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8 text-[#D4AF37]\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"m12 3 1.912 5.813a2 2 0 0 0 1.275 1.275L21 12l-5.813 1.912a2 2 0 0 0-1.275 1.275L12 21l-1.912-5.813a2 2 0 0 0-